it.univr.terapiaintensiva.model

Interface CsvWritable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Administration, Alarm, AlarmOff, Patient, Person, Prescription, Vitals, VitalsLog

    public interface CsvWritable
    Guarantees compatibility with csv format. All classes that have to perform operations with csv files must implement this interface.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Static Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      static java.lang.String csvFormat()
      This format must be written on first line of each csv file.
      java.lang.String toCsv()
      String returned contains class fields that must respect the csv format of the class.

    • Method Detail

      • csvFormat

        static java.lang.String csvFormat()
        This format must be written on first line of each csv file. All classes that implement CsvWritable must implement an own csvFormat() method based on class fields.
        Returns:
        String rapresenting the order of values in records of csv file.

      • toCsv

        java.lang.String toCsv()
        String returned contains class fields that must respect the csv format of the class.
        Returns:
        String of values comma-separated.
